##Cry of sadness | ECMO used for more than 30 days, still can not save old classmates!

Sh-scalpel

Functional introduction, Shanghai Medical Surgical cattle gathering place, your side of the surgical experts.

Expert Clinic | rational drug use | focus | surgery day | medical history

Medical history
Today's medical history is tomorrow's medical history

Press
The nightmare comes again, our heart is as dry as chaff, the face is as dead ash, have no words to ask the sky.

My classmate Jiang Xueqing, head of thyroid surgery at Wuhan Central Hospital, has just died of a coronavirus infection.

He is so tenacious that experts have worked hard to save him for more than 40 days and are still unable to save him.

He contracted Wuhan Coronavirus at work and was hospitalized on January 17. Experts from all sides, the use of the means are used, ECMO used for more than 30 days, still can not save the old classmate.

Blood pressure dropped yesterday, probably due to an infection that's hard to control, although we tried a lot of antibiotics. Our class invited Jiang Xueqing's daughter into the class to discuss her father's illness in the last days, so we know the development of the illness, but also mentally prepared.

Jiang Xueqing, an American returned from overseas, returned to practice medicine in Wuhan after studying at the prestigious Baylor College of Medicine. We also spoke on the phone while he was at Thewes. He had won a national award for his medical skills, he is the "warm male doctor" in the heart of patients.

Wish the old schoolmate all the way to go well, eight in those days of the roommate less one, he left too early, to the football player's body. There is no virus, no infection in heaven.

This is a message I wrote to Jiang Xueqing's daughter: "I just woke up from sleep and lost my roommate. I will never come back with my voice, my smile, and the Mandarin of the Honggang city. You and your mother have done your best. I am sorry and take care. "

Harvard Medical School Student Tongji Medical College

According to reports, Jiang Xueqing is the only national "Chinese physician award" winner in the field of breast. In 2018, the physician sent out a video of him.

Wuhan's Central Hospital, where Dr Chiang hok-hing Works, screams with pathos
